{
  "page": "Knight of Ninestars",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Knight of Ninestars</b> is the title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">House Templeton</a>, a powerful and ancient house of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>, seated at the eponymous castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Ninestars\" title=\"Ninestars\">Ninestars</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Knights_of_Ninestars\">Known Knights of Ninestars</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Knight_of_Ninestars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Knights of Ninestars\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Luceon_Templeton\" title=\"Luceon Templeton\">Luceon Templeton</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> knight who fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Seven_Stars\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of Seven Stars\">Battle of Seven Stars</a>.</li>\n<li>An unidentified <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Ninestars_(First_Blackfyre_Rebellion)\" title=\"Knight of Ninestars (First Blackfyre Rebellion)\">Knight of Ninestars</a>, killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon Blackfyre</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Redgrass_Field\" title=\"Battle of the Redgrass Field\">Battle of the Redgrass Field</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Templeton\" title=\"Symond Templeton\">Symond Templeton</a>, the current Knight of Ninestars.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Knight_of_Ninestars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Cersei IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404112055\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 122/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8578/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 693/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 58/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion 